Sector 7 Space Laboratories Fuel Station 71 with Crew Transporter

If you haven't had a chance to do any docking yet it is a challenge like no other and so much fun! it took quite a few tries and had very little fuel to spare, my propellant was out and had to use the mains to dock. I am posting images and details about the Transporter on the next post.
